Assignment No.6 
Use any loop

Q1. Write a program to calculate sum of first N natural numbers
Ans: #include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int i=1,n,s=0;
    printf("Enter a number");
    scanf("%d",&n);
    while(i<=n)
    {
       	s=s+i;
       	++i;
    }
    printf("\nSum is %d",s);
    return 0;
}

Q2. Write a program to calculate sum of first N even natural numbers
Ans: #include<stdio.h>
int main()
